name: Ready to Play!- MEtaverse. 02
description: I'm stuck in the world of the popular metaverse. The creator created this scene in 2045 when the real world conditions were no longer interesting to enjoy. All trapped in an imaginary world that looks interesting. But still, the imaginary world is the creator's imagination. I have to follow the creator's line of thought and solve the puzzle. Which in the end the expression that the real world exists and is more beautiful. I'm not playing as the main character, I'm just participating.
